title.rendered: Windsor Brokers Awards the Winners of the Ultimate Trading Challenge

content.rendered:
Windsor Brokers Awards Cash Prizes to the Winners of the Ultimate Trading Challenge

Windsor Brokers’ traders battled to climb up the ranks in the Ultimate Trading Challenge for a chance to win $180,000 in withdrawable cash prizes. From September 2022 until March 2023, the 10 traders with the highest ROIs on their trading activity got cash prizes from the $30,000 monthly cash prize pool.

This sixth-month contest was a major success for both the winners of the competition and the company. The volume of interest and participation proved to us that our community of traders are always ready for a challenge.

Participants from all corners of the world put their skills to the test, going head-to-head for the cash prizes! In the end, 60 winners were awarded withdrawable cash prizes but only one knocked the rest of the competition out with a whopping 6,341% ROI!

We would like to congratulate all the winners on their victories! You have proven that your skills and technique are worthy of the Ultimate Trader title.

We would also like to extend a very special thank you to all the participants. It is amazing to see that we have such talented traders in our community!

We look forward to seeing what you do next time!

View Winners
